title: RHONJ Reunion! + Jake Borelli from Grey's Anatomy
itunes:title: RHONJ Reunion! + Jake Borelli from Grey's Anatomy
description:
Danny recaps the first part of the thrilling Real Housewives of New Jersey reunion, which came in hot!!! After the Housewives chat, Jake Borelli, one of the stars of Grey's Anatomy, stops by to talk about the 400th episode, what it was like to join the iconic show, gay representation, and more!


Jake Borelli Interview: 22:00ish


BOOK: Smarturl.it/unremember
